Revision history for Git-CPAN-Hook

0.02 2011-06-09
        [FEATURES]
        - new 'init' command, to simplify the initial configuration of
          CPAN repository
        [TESTS]
        - tests now cover the 'init' command
        - tested to work with git from version 1.5.0 to 1.7.5.2

0.01 2011-05-14
        [FEATURES]
        - proof-of-concept for putting your CPAN install under git control
        - only works with CPAN.pm
        - created during the Perl QA Hackathon 2011

